metadata.name: Love And Flower #1
metadata.description:
There will be no more war filled with sorrow. There will be no war that causes people to lose their happiness. There will be no bullets, no bombs, no blood. 

They will put in petals instead of bullets. Only flowers will be in full bloom on every side. 

Wish you have lots of love and full of happiness always...

--

Resolution : 250 DPI
